(1+x)^n = \sum_{k=0}^n \dbinom{n}k x^k
\left. \dfrac{(1+x)^{n+1}}{n+1} \right \vert_{0}^1 = \sum_{k=0}^n \dbinom{n}k \left. \dfrac{x^{k+1}}{k+1} \right \vert_0^1
